    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's not about resting though. it's not like a burnout where you just need a nap or a new hobby. it feels more like the core of me is just... gone. like the version of me that actually mattered is extinct. why keep going through the motions if the thing that made me \"me\" is dead? it just feels like dragging a corpse around.",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
